Package: nattunnel
Version: @VERSION@
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: wireguard-tools, iproute2
Maintainer: milesthenerd
Homepage: https://github.com/milesthenerd/NATTunnel
Description: Mesh VPN daemon with NAT hole-punching
 NATTunnel creates WireGuard tunnels between peers behind NAT, using a
 mediation server to coordinate UDP hole-punching. Peers form a fully
 decentralized mesh where every peer can reach every other peer.
